HEADWORD: Carabus
<hw>Car"a*bus</hw> <pr>(k⟦acr⟧r"⟦adot⟧*b⟦ucr⟧s)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>ka`rabos</grk> a horned beetle.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of ground beetles, including numerous
species. They devour many injurious insects.</def>⟦br⟧
